timeline.bodyText:
@jamezp
I'm not sure what this item was meant for in this file. Probably it can be removed, as AIUI the version string is meant to be controlled from the pom. But I note that it's quasi-camel-case here, and elsewhere in the adoc files, while the pom uses lower case, as does the README note on using it:
https://github.com/wildfly/wildfly/blob/master/docs/pom.xml#L69
